Enkata e nkiting'oto


1   “Ore akenya te ina kata naa kedumunye Mikael, ilo kitok oitore iltung'ana linono. Naa kelotu enkata e nyamali, neitu ae kata etumi ebaiki apa meetae olorere o metabaiki ina kata; kake ore inakata naa kepuoi aakordu iltung'ana linono, pooki ng'ae otumi enkarna enye eigero ti atua embuku. 
2   Ore ilkumok le lelo ooirurate ti atua enterit e nkop neinyototo, ore kulikae nedumakino enkishui nemeiting, ore ilkulikae naa enkurruna o esulare oo ntarasi. 
3  Ore lelo ng'eni newang'u anaa ewang'an e shumata; ore lelo ooboiniki ilkumok enkoitoi oosipat newang'u anaa ilakir ntarasi o ntarasi. 
4   Kake ore iyie Daniel, tunuka lelo rorei; nimishir aiken ina buku, o metabau enkata e nkiting'oto Keyooki ilkumok aakuet nekuetu, naa keponari eng'eno.”


5  Ore nanu Daniel naing'orisho, naa ng'ura, eitashe kulikae oare, obo tele kekun e olkeju o likae te lido kekun o lkeju. 
6  Najoki nanu ilo tung'ani oishopo too nkilani naapuyiapui, ilo otii shumata eilo keju, “Kenkata nabaa pee ebau enkiting'oto e kuna baa e nking'asia?” 
7   Ore ilo tung'ani oishopo too nkilani naapuyiapui, ilo otii shumata nena ariak e olkeju nedumu enkaina enye e tatene o enkaina enye e kedienye aipirie shumata; naning nanu ninye einos olmumai teilo oishu ntarasi nchere te nkata, o inkatitin are, o lpisiai le nkata; naa te neidip ninche aatigil engolon e lelo tung'ana sinyat aaiting'ie ore kuna baa pooki neaku eitabayioki. 
8  Atoning'o nanu kake eitu aning'u ayiolou. Najo nanu, “Olaitoriani lai, kainyoo akenya epuo kuna baa aaku.” 
9  Nejo ninye, “Shomo enkoitoi ino Daniel, amu eikenoyioki lelo rorei nemishiri o metabau enkata e nkiting'oto. 
10   Keipok ilkumok ate, neiborrie ate, nesilayu; kake ore lelo arruok neasisho te nkarruisho; nemeetae obo le lelo arruok olo aning'u; kake ore lelo ng'eni naa kepuo aaning'u. 
11   Naa ore ebaiki ina kata neiwuang'ieki ilo asar opejori anaake aaitasheyie ilo minong le mijoonisho, naa keaku nkolong'i enkalifu nabo, o iip are o ntomoni naaudo. 
12  Emayiana ilo oanyisho nelotu nena olong'i enkalifu, iip uni o tomoni uni. 
13  Kake shomo enkoitoi ino o metabau enkiting'oto; amu ilo ayeng'iyeng'a, nilo aitashe te wueji ino negeluno te nkiting'oto e nena olong'i.”

